Package com.attendace.dao.handlers

Class DefaultHandler

java.lang.Object
com.attendace.dao.Handler
com.attendace.dao.handlers.DefaultHandler
public class DefaultHandler extends Handler
The DefaultHandler class acts as the entry point for the Chain of Responsibility pattern. This handler does not process any requests and always returns false in canProcess. Its main purpose is to provide a starting node for the chain and to delegate all requests to the next handler in the chain.
